Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Question}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.23,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Ta-daah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.23,0:00:06.49,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,I will be presenting today’s PokéProblem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.49,0:00:12.58,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Today we see Kapu-Kokeko’s Z-Move; “___ de Alola.” \N What is the first word?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.58,0:00:15.50,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Get the answer at the end of the episode!
Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.70,0:00:20.25,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The battle between Satoshi and Professor Kukui \N grew ever more intense,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.25,0:00:23.38,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and Nyaheat finally \N managed to defeat Gaogaen.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.38,0:00:29.30,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But immediately after Nyaheat evolved \N into Gaogaen himself, he ran out of strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.39,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,As Professor Kukui was about to \N send out his final Pokémon,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.39,0:00:38.18,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko made an unexpected appearance, \N and requested a battle with Satoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.18,0:00:41.69,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! \N We don’t mind! Let’s do this!{Copy-paste from 143 スタート}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.57,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,This just got really interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.57,0:00:46.94,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.94,0:00:51.32,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,How about all of you? \N Do you want to see Kapu-Kokeko battle?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.83,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let me fight with this guy first!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.92,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Competitor Satoshi rises \N to the challenge with Agoyon!{Copy-paste from 143 ストップ}{I can no longer remember if this was deliberate but... RIIIIIIIISE IF YOU'RE PREPARED FOR THE CHALLENGE[/dub] -Starfish OF THE FUTURE}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.29,0:01:08.21,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Alola’s mightiest combo; Melemele Island’s \N Guardian Deity Kapu-Kokeko and Professor Kukui...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.21,0:01:13.39,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Their battle with Satoshi and \N the Ultra Beast Agoyon is about to start!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.22,0:01:20.39,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,The entire battlefield has become \N Electric Field!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.52,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,It’s like a sea of electricity!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.52,0:01:27.03,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,In Electric Field, \N Electric-type moves become stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.03,0:01:31.03,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! If we’re gonna \N fight together, we gotta win!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.03,0:01:31.90,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.99,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! Let’s go \N at full power, Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.45,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Sludge Bomb!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.96,0:01:42.46,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Dodge it, Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.96,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Steel Wing, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.29,0:01:47.46,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Scissor Cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.26,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Use Steel Wing again!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.22,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What speed! What power!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.22,0:02:04.56,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Is this the power possessed by \N an Ultra Beast and a Guardian Deity?!
Comment: 10,0:02:07.48,0:02:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 10,0:03:35.49,0:03:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.21,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Scissor Cross again!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.34,0:03:54.71,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Magical Shine!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.02,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Steel Wing!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.73,0:04:10.98,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dragon Pulse!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.69,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.69,0:04:16.28,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Dragon-type moves have no effect on \N the Fairy-type Kapu-Kokeko-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.97,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,He used the Dragon Pulse \N to blind them!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.39,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Satoshi shocks!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.01,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,That’s just like him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.52,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Impressive...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.10,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! Magical Shine!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.89,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Sludge Bomb!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.69,0:04:53.94,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Then charge straight in!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.86,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Discharge!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.74,0:05:00.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,{\an8}100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.59,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.14,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Agoyon is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.72,0:05:30.73,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko, the Guardian Deity from \N the Ruins of Conflict, truly lives up to the legends!{SASUGA -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.73,0:05:34.98,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Is its astonishing power and speed \N utterly unmatched?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.94,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko is strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.99,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,But Agoyon sure fought hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.49,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes! We should applaud \N Agoyon, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.37,Main,Kaki & Mamane,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.75,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.75,0:05:58.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’m really glad I got to battle with you \N in the Alola League.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.81,0:06:21.11,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,The young Ultra Beast’s power was no match for \N the experience of the Alolan Guardian Deity, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.24,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it, \N Professor Kukui!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.28,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,Or rather, Royal Mask!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.99,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu! It’s all on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.83,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Both men are now down to \N their final Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.21,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Pikachu versus Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.21,0:06:46.80,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Whoever wins this fight will be \N the winner of this spectacular exhibition match!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.56,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Let the battle begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.32,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu! 100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.36,0:07:03.19,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Charge in with Magical Shine!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.92,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Pikachu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.54,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.67,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.22,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Magical Shine!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.10,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Dodge it, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.15,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Iron Tail!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.95,0:07:51.49,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,Pikachu scores a hit \N with Iron Tail!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.54,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko! \N Use Nature’s Madness!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.29,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Guard with Electric Net!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.68,0:08:11.80,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lightning Speed!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.44,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.35,Main,Hau,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Electric Net!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.87,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.29,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.54,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Discharge!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.10,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.07,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.49,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You’ve gotten stronger!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.62,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Just over the past few days \N battling in the League...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.95,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,{\t(2855,3355,\3c&HFFFFFF&)}You’ve shown rapid growth!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.25,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You hear that, Pikachu?! \N We’ve gotten stronger!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.81,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.77,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You mean you wanna use a Z-Move?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.02,0:09:47.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I just used up \N my Z-Move with Gaogaen.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.41,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.41,0:10:01.21,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,What is this? \N Kapu-Kokeko has started singing!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.87,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon!
Comment: 10,0:10:40.54,0:10:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.14,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,The Kapu have assembled!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.31,Main,Sauboh,0,0,0,,What an exquisite harmony!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.81,Main,Wicke,0,0,0,,I feel romanticism in the air!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.87,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,A Kapu shower!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.54,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s like a rainbow!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.34,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It’s so warm!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Did the Guardian Deities \N share their power with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.15,0:11:49.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.15,0:11:53.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,So, now I can use it again?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.25,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.04,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,...a Kapu-Z?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.42,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,What?! A Kapu-Z?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.17,0:12:14.21,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,The Guardian Deities’ exclusive Z-Move, \N spoken of in ancient folklore!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.01,0:12:21.22,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,The legendary Z-Move they say the Kapu fired alongside \N a great hero, to save Alola in its time of need...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.31,0:12:28.06,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You mean you want to \N use {\i1}that{\i0} Z-Move, here, now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.56,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Now this is getting \N really interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.57,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.95,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I will fire a Z-Move \N with Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.74,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You and Pikachu fire one, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.45,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Will you win...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.20,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,...or will Kapu-Kokeko and I win?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.96,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,It’ll be a full power versus \N full power showdown!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.54,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,A full power versus full power...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.38,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,...showdown?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.21,0:12:59.05,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s great, Professor! I love it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.05,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.27,0:13:13.56,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,The legendary move passed on \N since ancient times...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.65,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Only when people, \N Pokémon and nature...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.82,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,...live together and share all,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.99,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,is the ultimate Z-Power born!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.41,Main,Hau,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.76,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.17,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,An earth...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.38,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,...titan?{This scene sorely lacks Guren no Yumiya. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.01,0:14:26.85,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Hang on! Satoshi is gonna \N have to fight that titan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.39,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,That’s way too big!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.52,0:14:31.14,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You can do it, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.89,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right. Let’s go, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.83,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s show them our full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Far greater than 100,000 Volts...{Copy-paste from 54 スタート}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,1,000,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.65,0:15:24.24,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,No, way, {\i1}way{\i0} greater than that! \N Our super full power!{Copy-paste from 54 ストップ}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.36,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.36,0:15:32.49,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Guardian de Alola!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.29,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,10,000,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.94,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This is our...{KA... ME... HA... ME... -Son Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,...full power!{HAAAAAAAAAA!!!! -Son Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.74,0:16:10.32,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.08,0:16:19.54,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu, can you feel...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.04,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,...the power of Alola?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.84,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We’ve felt this power so many times \N while we’ve been here in Alola!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.55,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Facing the Island Pilgrimage \N Trials and Grand Trials...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.52,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Meeting plenty of Pokémon...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.52,0:16:39.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Having loads of battles \N with our new friends and rivals...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.73,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We could always feel \N the power of Alola!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Now it’s time to become one \N with that power!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.75,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.90,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.36,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,As such, the winner is \N Competitor Satoshi!{not gonna lie, I didn’t expect this at all -Puto}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.25,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,They did it-roto! \N They won-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.76,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Satoshi won!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.76,0:18:32.34,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He beat Professor Kukui \N and Kapu-Kokeko!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.76,0:18:34.13,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He won, Lilie!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.47,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes, he did!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.97,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He won, Kaki! Mao! Suiren!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.85,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I’m so moved!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.64,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.48,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Satoshi, the ultimate Champion!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.57,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Satoshi, you did it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.44,Main,Hau,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Satoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.95,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We won...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.41,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.25,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.21,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.01,0:19:18.89,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,The Alola Pokémon League Champion, \N Competitor Satoshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.89,0:19:24.56,Main,Jeekyo,0,0,0,,...has also triumphed in his exhibition match \N with Competitor Kukui!{I mean, generally speaking I feel like winning the League itself should have been the bigger accomplishment here, but... Yeah no Gladio ain’t got NOTHING on Kukui. Not even BEFORE Kukui teamed up with a LITERAL GOD. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.28,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kapu-Tetefu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.04,0:19:47.04,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You did it, Pikachu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.97,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.24,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.57,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Thank you. \N That was an incredible battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.67,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kapu-Kokeko, \N Professor Kukui!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.26,0:20:37.05,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.59,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Could this battle have been...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.59,0:20:43.81,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,...Kapu-Kokeko’s Grand Trial \N for young Satoshi{honorific note: Satoshi-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.85,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,No, I suppose it could be seen as \N a final exam!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.69,Main,Burnet & Hanako,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.19,Main,Burnet & Hanako,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.90,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mom! Professor Burnet!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.49,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,You, too, Pika-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.62,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,That was a superb battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.62,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,You were so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.62,0:21:10.33,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Yeah! You were incredible, Satoshi! \N And Kukui{honorific note: Kukui-kun}, so were you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.80,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,That was a great League, \N wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.56,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Alola Pokémon League \N was the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.10,0:21:28.10,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.10,0:21:33.19,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,But the real “best” here \N are you guys, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We sure are!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.15,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Hey! Don’t get cocky!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.28,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,But I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.45,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Man, you guys are just...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.79,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Following their victory \N in the Alola Pokémon League,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.79,0:21:52.54,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi, Pikachu, and the team have won \N their exhibition match against Professor Kukui, as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.50,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.92,Main,Narrator,300,0,0,,Congratulations, \N Pikachu!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.51,0:21:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.50,0:23:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.17,0:23:24.97,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.97,0:23:29.39,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,Kapu-Kokeko’s Z-Move was \N “Guardian de Alola”!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.39,0:23:37.90,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,The legendary Z-Move Kapu-Kokeko unleashed with Kukui, \N Guardian de Alola, defied imagination, did it not?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.94,Main,Hala,0,0,0,,A power befitting of our Guardian Deity!{SASUGA -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.53,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,That really was quite the show!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.41,Main,Hanako,0,0,0,,Professor, we should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.12,0:23:54.66,Main,Okido,0,0,0,,Ms. Burnet{honorific note: Burnet-san}, could you please \N give Satoshi our regards?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.66,0:23:56.04,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.54,0:23:57.62,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Take care.
Comment: 10,0:24:00.54,0:24:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.13,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What could be wrong \N with Professor Kukui?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.67,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,He’s been like this since yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.05,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Does he have burnout?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.05,0:24:09.59,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Post-League melancholy, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.59,0:24:11.55,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Professor! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.81,Main,Them,0,0,0,,Give us some battle training!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.81,0:24:13.85,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.85,0:24:14.72,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,For next year!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.72,0:24:16.06,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Next year...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.06,0:24:18.31,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Of course! Next year!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.31,0:24:20.73,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.73,0:24:23.23,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,The Sun, the Moon, and Our Dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.23,0:24:26.78,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Yeah! Alola’s second Pokémon League!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.49,0:24:29.11,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good grief...{\i0}{Gimme a break...}
