Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.57,0:02:11.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:11.99,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
