Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.63,OP,,0,0,0,,You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.63,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.63,0:02:35.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:35.39,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}{\be3\bord9}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.89,OP,,0,0,0,,Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.89,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.89,0:02:45.14,OP,,0,0,0,,will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:45.14,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.48,OP,,0,0,0,,Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.48,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.57,OP,,0,0,0,,playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.57,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.57,0:02:54.57,OP,,0,0,0,,go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:54.57,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.78,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.78,0:03:03.66,OP,,0,0,0,,how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:03.66,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.66,0:03:08.08,OP,,0,0,0,,Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:08.08,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.08,0:03:13.97,OP,,0,0,0,,Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:13.97,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.97,0:03:17.84,OP,,0,0,0,,Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:17.84,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.84,0:03:22.93,OP,,0,0,0,,With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:22.93,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.94,OP,,0,0,0,,It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.94,0:03:35.49,OP,,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:35.49,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:35.49,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=3}
