Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.83,0:14:57.29,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,How long has it been since I bid Masara Town farewell?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.38,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Got so many cuts, scratches, and friends
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.72,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I’m kinda proud of that
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.84,0:15:09.64,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,The sneakers I rushed out to buy \N back when they were the latest trend...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.85,0:15:16.56,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,...are now one of a kind, no others like them in the world
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.56,0:15:23.19,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,They’re the best worn-out shoes around!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.49,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Before I know it... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.66,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Little by little... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.58,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I’m gonna become... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.58,0:15:44.13,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,...way stronger than I am! Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.81,0:16:00.27,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I don’t need a suitcase, photos, or a guide on this journey
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.23,0:16:06.57,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,but I’ll keep the warmth of everyone I’ve met as a souvenir!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.78,0:16:12.78,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I had some really harsh memories along the way, too
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.51,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Before I know it... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.72,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Little by little... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.73,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I’m gonna become... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.81,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,...so much more! Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.73,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Before I know it... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.78,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,Little by little... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.57,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,I’m gonna become... Type: Wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.57,0:17:38.41,Insert,Type: Wild,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}...way stronger than I am! Type: Wild!
